# TODO: create a Kokkos GPU production input from prod.in
# - use package kokkos and atom_style atomic/kk
# - use pair_style metatomic/kk and run_style verlet/kk
# - read_restart npt.restart

units metal
atom_style atomic/kk

read_restart npt.restart

pair_style metatomic/kk &
    model.pt &
    uncertainty_threshold off &
    device cuda

pair_coeff * * 1 8

neighbor 2.0 bin
timestep 0.0005

thermo 100

fix 1 all nve
dump traj all custom 100 prod-kk.lammpstrj id type x y z
dump_modify traj sort id

run_style verlet/kk
run 1000
